# mcptools — suggestions

When a service, agent, or startup check finds an anomaly, call **`SuggestionService`** — do not only log.

```javascript
const { capture, captureIf, makeFingerprint } = require('../services/SuggestionService');

await captureIf(condition, {
  orgId,
  userId,
  source: 'serviceName',
  category: 'alert',
  fingerprint: makeFingerprint('serviceName', 'stable-key'),
  title: '…',
  body: '…',
  context: '…',
});
```

See `knowledge_base/architecture/SUGGESTIONS_INBOX.md`.
